Yes Kamala sucked and was retarded.

So if a Democrat promises "more free stuff" it will be met with bigger backlash than ever before by voters who see it as leading us off a financial cliff to our national doom.

And even if Democrats promise "more taxes on the rich" it won't even be enough to close the deficit!

So how could it possibly be enough to give out more free stuff?

The one thing that seems to unify all Democrats is their desire to mooch off of everybody else.

Now that "more free shit" is impossible to win an election on, due to the financial cliff in front of us, the Democrats have nothing to offer low information voters.

The only exception is the radicals who show up to vote for tranny rights or something, which is not popular with average people.

My prediction: The Democrats as we know it will be destroyed by their inability to run on "free shit" anymore.
